title.rendered: NEWTECONS COMMENCED THE PEGASUITE II – A PROJECT FOR A CLASSY CUSHY LIFE

content.rendered:
On October 06, 2020, Phu Gia Real Estate Investment Company Limited (Owner) and Newtecons as the General Contractor accomplished the Commencement Ceremony of The Pegasuite II project located in Ward 6, District 8, Ho Chi Minh City.

Developed by Phuong Viet Investment Joint Stock Company (PVInvest), The Pegasuite II is a high-rise apartment complex with 28 upground floors and 1 basement, including simplexes, duplexes, duplexes with garden, shophouses, officetels among other properties. This youthful designed, comfortable and modern building is an ideal living space for young families who desire for a dream home amid the hustle of Ho Chi Minh City

At the ceremony, Mr. Le Minh Tuan – Chairman of PVInvest – conveyed his confidence in the selection of construction contractor for the project. “I see what Newtecons aspires. Newtecons has made its brand more and more known to every corner of the country. I believe they would soon become among leading contractors in the construction industry”, said Mr. Tuan.

In reply to sincere words of Mr. Tuan, Mr. Tran Kim Long – Newtecons General Director – delivered his heartfelt thanks. He is completely confident in the competency of Newtecons to satisfy the Owner’s expectations. The project success, above all, is an important premise for the desirable long-lasting cooperation between the two parties.
